Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form
greetings, our ads have been In review for  1 week. can you please assist

Hi there! I'm sorry to hear that your ads have been in review for a week. Could you please let me know if this is a new account and if your business has been verified? This will help me provide more specific assistance.
not sure, how do we verify

No worries! To verify your account, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners.

Great! Since you've already submitted the verification details, it might just be a matter of time before your ads get reviewed. If it's been over a week, I recommend following up with our support team to check on the status. You can email them at adsupport@newsbreak.com and mention that your ads have been in review for over a week. They should be able to provide you with an update.
ive emailed support many times, no response

I'm sorry to hear that you haven't received a response from support. Let me help you out. Could you please provide more details about the issue you're facing? This way, I can assist you better or escalate it accordingly.
